Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.32,1:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth then, is dependent upon context.\NThere is no truth independent of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.67,1:11:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,context.\NTruth is only true within a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.48,1:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,context.\NIn a different context, it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.19,1:11:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll get you a badge in one context\Nwill get you executed in another. The
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.84,1:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,context makes all the difference. So\Nmeaning and significance cannot be
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.12,1:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,derived from this. Only by this within\Nthis field here, within this field it's
