Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.12,1:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as truth stated\Nwithout context. Context is usually
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.64,1:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,implied\Nbut not specifically stated. This is the
