Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.64,1:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,intentionality and okay on your part and\Nnow it's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.76,1:13:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Until without this field here, no\Npotentiality could become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.23,1:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because prior to divinity, prior to\NGod is the Godhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.76,1:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is out of the unmanifest that the\Nmanifest arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.19,1:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the unmanifest arises the\Nmanifest
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.64,1:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the potentiality becomes the\Nactuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.60,1:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has within it the power nothing\Nin here has the power of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.15,1:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very weak field. Anything here\Ncan knock this out altogether.
