Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.08,1:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that instead of a barren tree, you\Nhave a tree full of leaves
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.60,1:15:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and abundance.\NAbundance is quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.04,1:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Abundance\Nis overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.36,1:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you begin to when you get to a\Ncertain point, everything just begins to
