Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.44,1:22:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was the\Nlotus sutra chanted in sense. Good. And
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.56,1:22:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is chanted today,\Nthey say we did it centuries ago
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.40,1:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're part of a brotherhood. Last\Ntime we were together was 350 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.84,1:22:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh there's one of the signals of the\Nmill membership.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.56,1:22:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We took an oath 350 years ago\Nand paid the price in this lifetime to
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.04,1:22:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,be free of it. Huh.\NNow we're dedicated to truth with no
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.60,1:23:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,name.\NI just got through writing an article
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.76,1:23:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for a\Ngoing to be out published in India.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.80,1:23:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,professorship there in India\Nand I'm adding a chapter of the book
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.84,1:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's dedicated to Dali Lala\Nand
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.48,1:23:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the first thing to know is that\Nthe Buddha was not a Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.15,1:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth transcends all denominations.\NAnd I always get a kick out of
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.40,1:23:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Christians who consider Buddha\Nuh to be uh
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.60,1:23:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what is he a heathen? Because he was\Nborn 500 years before Jesus. So how
