Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.19,1:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,take on any questions and uh answer them\Nto the best of our ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.48,1:24:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, within a certain paradigm of\Nreality.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.23,1:24:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hello.\N>> Um, my name is Liz and I'm from Toronto,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.00,1:24:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Canada. Very grateful to be here.\N>> My question is about the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.80,1:24:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,between want, want and intention. You\Nsaid earlier that to want something is
