Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.32,1:24:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And I I've read two schools of thought.\NI'm thinking of Deepak Chopra who talks
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.44,1:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about introducing intention into the\Nfield. And I was just browsing in the
